text: Östermalm is a borough (stadsdelsområde) in central Stockholm,Sweden. It is named after the dominating district. Except Östermalm (proper) there are four districts in the borough: Djurgården, Hjorthagen, Ladugårdsgärdet (popularly known as Gärdet), and Norra Djurgården. Note that a portion of northern Östermalm is organized in Norrmalm borough. The population is 61,253 on an area of 18.00 km², which gives a density of 3,402.94/km². ==See also== *Norra Djurgårdsstaden ==References== ==External links== Category:Boroughs of Stockholm hu:Östermalm (kerület)
